11:
You always had a stubborn streak,
Zegra! You never knew when to GIVE
UP!
18:
We did it! Alk... Marina...
We actually did it!
24:
Luca... Your voice just now... I could
hear it in my head—
29: Uh oh. This is... not good, is it?
32: It's just like the time with the squid!
37:
What do we do? We have to get out
of here! Wait, where's Belsidia?
42:
The Wicked Witch of the Rift... Why is
she coming after me?!
50:
I see... So you were doing your
experiments on dragons...
52:
Listen here. I like to stir the pot and
cause chaos just as much as the
next witch... But you...
55:
You hurt my Alky-Walky...
And THAT is where I draw the line!
62:
From the depths of chaos arise...
Abyss Pierce!
71:
Or, wait a minute. Isn't this the same
place as before? Are we going in
circles?!
76:
Crap, crap, crap! What do we do?!
We have to get out of here!
Someone think of something!
85:
You're right... It's better to face our
inevitable demise with calm
resignation.
88:
What happened to all your
confidence from before?!
93:
Luca's right, let's stop panicking and
breathe! Okay, think, Alk, think! What
could we do... in a situation... like
this...?
106:
Guess who! It's a-me! ...Lia. Did you
forget about me?
110:
Come to think of it, you definitely
forgot about me—you didn't even
take me on your vacation to the
beach! I'm a mermaid, Alk! That's
what I do, I swim!
119:
You really went and gave us a scare
there, Alk. You have to cut that out,
for real.
124:
We should count ourselves lucky
that everyone made it back alive!
131:
Indeed! "A true knight always returns
home victorious," as they say! A
splendid job, everyone!
136:
Hah-hah! Excellent to see us all
unscathed! Though I may have lost
sensation in my knees—I know not
how much longer they will bear my
weight!
139:
I'm not sure you know what
"unscathed" means, mister prince.
Anyway, I guess you guys did an
OKAY job staying alive, all things
considered.
143:
She ridicules, even as she bears
open her heart. I'm starting to
understand you, little princess! How
GORGEOUS!
146:
I am grateful to the Stars for guiding
you all back home safely. Make sure
to get enough rest, you hear?
149:
No kidding, lady luck really smiled
on you lot today. Though maybe it
wasn't all luck, heh.
155:
Everyone's so happy! Which means
I'm super happy, too! I'm gonna be
the happiest person here!
159:
Oh? I highly doubt you can find a
way to be happier than even me,
Illumine! I've been reunited with my
Alky-Walky!
164:
I'm beyond glad to see you all return
safely. But I must admit I did not
much enjoy being left behind like
that...
180: I've caused you all so much trouble—
186:
Trouble? What are you talking
about, kid? No such thing!
194: I mean, we had a BLAST, didn't we?
200: I... I guess... I had a lot of fun, too!
204:
So Luca, what do you have planned
next? All of Captain Zegra's valuable
research is still contained in that
crystal, right?
207:
Yes. To be honest, I'm not sure what
to do with something as dangerous
as this. I'd like to get some advice...
209:
But this really IS valuable
knowledge. There are probably tons
of ways to make effective use of it. I
might even be able to make some
money off of it!
212:
Money, huh? Good to see you're
considering all your options.
215:
I mean, it's an inheritance, right? I
intend to make full use of whatever
father left me, and not a drop more.
221:
How assertive! You might even
make a good pirate, Luca!
225:
Marina... One day, when I become
stronger... Can I come see you again?
229:
Of course you can!
You don't even have to wait until
then—come anytime!
233:
Hey Alk... Is she always this...
welcoming?
237:
Heh, I think everyone in the Crimson
Blades is like this!
240:
I see... So it's not that I'm special or
anything...
243:
All remaining passengers please
board immediately! We'll be
departing soon!
256:
You're really cool, you know that?
Almost as cool as Marina.
262:
I don't know what I did to deserve
praise like that!
265:
Well, I guess it's time for us to be
heading back too!
To Starview Village!
275:
We haven't relaxed enough. Our
vacation is not over yet.
285:
I just got here, so I haven't been able
to do anything at all! If you leave
now, who will I hang out with?!
289:
All right, all right. Just make sure
nobody sees you, Amelia!
293:
Well then. I guess we can extend our
vacation a few more days! I think
we've earned it.
